    "summary": "Today People Incorporated, formerly IAC (Nasdaq: IAC), announced its legal name change and that the Company's common stock, listed on the Nasdaq Capital Market, will begin trading under the new ticker symbol PPLI, effective at market open today June 4, 2026. People Incorporated is the public entity that owns America's largest publisher People Inc., and a significant minority stake in MGM Resorts International.",
